title: BRIEF-Supermicro Announces Hearings Panel Date And Nasdaq Listing Extension
text:
April 5, 2018 / 1:11 PM / Updated 10 minutes ago BRIEF-Supermicro Announces Hearings Panel Date And Nasdaq Listing Extension Reuters Staff 
April 5 (Reuters) - Super Micro Computer Inc: 
* SUPERMICRO® ANNOUNCES HEARINGS PANEL DATE AND NASDAQ LISTING EXTENSION 
* SUPER MICRO COMPUTER INC - HEARING WILL TAKE PLACE ON APRIL 26, 2018 
* SUPER MICRO COMPUTER INC - ALSO ANNOUNCED THAT PANEL GRANTED COMPANY’S REQUEST TO EXTEND AUTOMATIC 15-DAY STAY OF SUSPENSION FROM NASDAQ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
